==Description==

The [[Image:Sketcher_SelectVerticalAxis.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_SelectVerticalAxis|Sketcher SelectVerticalAxis]] tool selects the vertical axis of the sketch.

==Usage==

# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Sketch → Sketcher tools → [[File:Sketcher_SelectVerticalAxis.svg|16px]] Select vertical axis}} option from the menu.
#* Right-click in the '''Elements''' section of the [[Sketcher_Dialog|Sketcher Dialog]] and select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Sketcher_SelectVerticalAxis.svg|16px]] Select Vertical Axis}} option from the context menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|Z}} then {{KEY|V}}.
# The vertical axis of the sketch is selected.


